  "texts": [
    "Codex, released in 2021, is the highest-researched LLM for code generation tasks included in 21.9% of all the studies analyzed in Figure 2.",
    "Another popular LLM is GPT-2 having an equal number of research papers as Codex, but was released in 2019 and indicates a stagnation or decrease in the number of papers since 2022.",
    "Another highly researched LLM is GPT-3, having 50 studies since 2020 and gaining popularity annually.",
    "The highest number of LLMs with the ability to generate code was released in 2023.",
    "In addition to RQ1.2."
  ]
}